The paper also introduces new Chaitin machines and discusses lambda calculus, which are relevant to the cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) sub-categories. Finally, the paper includes an algorithm for restricting the domain of blank-endmarker machines, which is related to data structures and could be relevant to the cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) sub-category.
